uot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5fb35cdd-630e-4046-996a-40eba2fded0c_1456x474.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p><strong>(IV) MCLOUD ‚ÄûGod Is Overrated‚Äú</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b273b5f4712f4bf473fe33c23864&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;GOD IS OVERRATED&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;McLoud&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/3PwjNf7UsXOKZoV3i2FaeA&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/3PwjNf7UsXOKZoV3i2FaeA" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>Jau 5tas McLoud≈≥ albumas. Kaip bƒóga laikas. Pavadinimas ‚ÄûDievas pervertintas‚Äú grƒÖ≈æina prie pirmojo - ‚ÄûDievo nuleisti‚Äú. Ir pasakoja, kaip Kristus randamas ka≈ækokiam afteryje Rusijoje. Kaip patys sakƒó LRT Opus, ‚Äûanksƒçiau kastruodavom gra≈æulius, dabar kastruojam ≈°ventuosius‚Äú. Tai tokie reikaliukai. McLoudai tƒôsia savo provokacijas, kurios visgi lieka pasi≈æaidimo, pasilinksminimo lygmeny ar bent taip yra priimamos jaunos publikos. Jei b≈´t≈≥ kiti laikai, gal visi drauge sudegint≈≥ kokio politiko ma≈°inƒÖ. Dabar gi grupƒó sako: ‚ÄûLietuva eina ƒØ priekƒØ, nes mes ≈°iƒÖ vasarƒÖ gyvenam i≈° miesto ≈°venƒçi≈≥.‚Äú ≈†itas paradoksalus faktas mane ir d≈æiugina (dƒól to, kad regionai sulaukia ≈°iek tiek daugiau ≈°iek tiek ƒØvairesnƒós muzikos nei anksƒçiau), ir kartu ka≈ækaip li≈´dina.</p><div><hr></div><p><strong>(V) NOYUS ‚ÄûSalva Xalva‚Äú</strong></p><div class="bandcamp-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://noyus.bandcamp.com/album/salva-xalva&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Salva Xalva, by Noyus&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;9 track album&quot;,&quot;thumbnail_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5e2f4547-5b8e-411a-af10-451299627cf4_700x700.jpeg&quot;,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;Noyus&quot;,&quot;embed_url&quot;:&quot;https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=1718871262/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/&quot;,&quot;is_album&quot;:true}" data-component-name="BandcampToDOM"><iframe src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=1718871262/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/" frameborder="0" gesture="media" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div><p>Jei ie≈°kote ≈°velnaus skambesio, li≈´dno ≈°okio, queer pop ar tiesiog ƒØkvƒópimo savaranki≈°kai kurti, Noyus ƒØra≈°ƒó labai asmeni≈°kƒÖ, trap≈≥ albumƒÖ apie vienatvƒô, meilƒós ie≈°kojimƒÖ ir bijojimƒÖ, geismƒÖ ir atsiribojimƒÖ. Singlas ‚ÄûIn Your Room‚Äú man yra viena gra≈æiausi≈≥ ≈°i≈≥ met≈≥ dain≈≥.</p><div id="youtube2-9QKm83BbyoI" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;9QKm83BbyoI&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/9QKm83BbyoI?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><div><hr></div><p><strong>(VI) DESPOTIN FAM ‚ÄûGeros naujienos‚Äú</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b273a636b3722441e27cd0702cdd&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;GEROS NAUJIENOS&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Despotin Fam, DJ Swix&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/65AxQyGn2IkZezXhD42EaC&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/65AxQyGn2IkZezXhD42EaC" frameborder="0" gesture="med