ges%2F8254b1ed-12ff-43fa-80c8-b8ead046574a_807x360.png" width="807" height="360" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8254b1ed-12ff-43fa-80c8-b8ead046574a_807x360.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:360,&quot;width&quot;:807,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:55563,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8254b1ed-12ff-43fa-80c8-b8ead046574a_807x360.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8254b1ed-12ff-43fa-80c8-b8ead046574a_807x360.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8254b1ed-12ff-43fa-80c8-b8ead046574a_807x360.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8254b1ed-12ff-43fa-80c8-b8ead046574a_807x360.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Jason (Founder of SaaStrfund) said - ‚ÄúI do get behind on email, but I love an amazing cold email and have funded maybe ~50% of my investments from them.&nbsp; I like an email pitch that is so amazing that I‚Äôd fund it just based on the email alone.&nbsp;‚Äú</p><p>So yes, is a perfect warm intro better?&nbsp; Yes.&nbsp; But even the top, most famous Seed VCs are hunting.&nbsp; Hunting unicorns and decacorns.&nbsp; And they can‚Äôt wait for them all to come from their networks.</p><p><em>Here‚Äôs the <strong>email from two startups to which <a href="https://x.com/jasonlk">Jason</a> gave million-dollar funding‚Ä¶</strong></em></p><blockquote><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d5fdb76-4a9f-41ed-b61a-1d266a2749eb_602x547.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d5fdb76-4a9f-41ed-b61a-1d266a2749eb_602x547.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d5fdb76-4a9f-41ed-b61a-1d266a2749eb_602x547.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d5fdb76-4a9f-41ed-b61a-1d266a2749eb_602x547.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7d5fdb76-4a9f-41ed-b61a-1d266a2749eb_602x547.webp 1