re></div></blockquote><p>So put together the very, very best cold email you can.&nbsp; Make it awesome in every way.&nbsp; And send it to your top VCs.&nbsp; At least seed and probably Series A VCs, too.\\</p><p>They may not respond.&nbsp; But if it‚Äôs awesome, including the title, I bet they open it.&nbsp; And if it‚Äôs super awesome, you have a better chance than you might think of getting a meeting.</p><div><hr></div><p><strong>Join 35000+ Founders, Investors and Startup Enthusiasts</strong> Getting Tactics To Build, Learn and Implement About Startups and Venture Capital.</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://theventurecrew.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;button-wrapper&quot;}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary button-wrapper" href="https://theventurecrew.substack.com/subscribe?"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h5><strong>THIS WEEK‚ÄôS NEWS RECAP</strong></h5><h4><strong>Major News In VC, Startup Funding &amp; Tech </strong></h4><ul><li><p>Perplexity Looking to Raise $500 Million at an $8B valuation. (<strong><a href="https://venturedailydigest.beehiiv.com/p/perplexity-looking-to-raise-at-8b-valuation-former-openai-cto-seeks-100m">Read Here</a></strong>) </p></li><li><p>Former OpenAI CTO Raising Over $100 Million For New AI Startup. (<strong><a href="https://venturedailydigest.beehiiv.com/p/perplexity-looking-to-raise-at-8b-valuation-former-openai-cto-seeks-100m">Read Here</a></strong>) </p></li><li><p>Byju‚Äôs, once India‚Äôs most valuable startup, is now effectively worth "zero," after raising $5 Billion. (<strong><a href="https://venturedailydigest.beehiiv.com/p/perplexity-looking-to-raise-at-8b-valuation-former-openai-cto-seeks-100m">Read Here</a></strong>) </p></li><li><p>Microsoft and OpenAI renegotiate multi-billion dollar partnership. (<strong><a href="https://venturedailydigest.beehi