line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><div><hr></div><h2>Stealth Founders ü•∑üèª</h2><h4><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/eduardo-alvarez-de-toledo/">Edu Alvarez de Toledo</a> üá™üá∏</h4><ul><li><p><strong>Experience</strong>: Boston Consulting Group, Fasty (Founder), Mango, Cruise</p></li><li><p><strong>Education</strong>: Stanford (MBA), Esade (BSc)</p></li></ul><h4><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohamed-abdelbary/">Mohamed Abdelbary</a> üá¨üáß</h4><ul><li><p><strong>Experience</strong>: Monzo Bank, Klivvr, DueDil, QuantumBlack</p></li><li><p><strong>Education</strong>: Oxford (MSc), The American University in Cairo (BSc)</p></li></ul><h4><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ahmedahres/">Ahmed Ares</a> üá¨üáß</h4><ul><li><p><strong>Experience</strong>: XYZ Reality, Heron Data, Revolut</p></li><li><p><strong>Education</strong>: EPFL (MSc), Eindhoven University of Technology (BSc)</p></li></ul><h4><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jenica-zhong/">Jenica Zhong</a> <strong>üá∫üá∏</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Experience</strong>: Palantir</p></li><li><p><strong>Education</strong>: Harvard (BSc)</p></li></ul><h4><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ahmedmedhatm/">Ahmed Medhat</a> <strong>üá∫üá∏</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Experience</strong>: Cold Spring Harbor Laboratory, Meta, DueDil, Oxford Internet Institute</p></li><li><p><strong>Education</strong>: Oxford (MSc), The American University in Cairo (BSc)</p></li></ul><h4><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/johnhinnegan/">John Hinnegan</a> <strong>üá∫üá∏</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Experience</strong>: Lumo (Co-Founder), Google, Amazon, Thinknear (Co-Founder, Acquired)</p></li><li><p><strong>Education</strong>: University of Waterloo (Bsc)</p></li></ul><div><hr></div><div><hr></div><h2>Early Startups üê£</h2><h4><strong><a href="https://ameba.ai">Ameba</a> </strong>üá¨üáß</h4><ul><li><p><strong>Industry: </strong>Supply Chain Logistics</p></li><li><p><strong>What they do: </strong>Ameba provides a supply chain solution powered by AI for real-time data analysis, automated supplier communication, and seamless integration with existing workflows, streamlining operations and simplifying processes. The main technologies used include AI for real-time data analysis, automated supplier communication, and seamless integration with existing workflows.</p></li><li><p><strong>Last Funding:</strong> Seed</p></li><li><p><strong>Total Funding: </strong>8‚Äô937‚Äô712 USD</p></li><li><p><strong>Notable Investors: </strong><a href="https://www.anamcaracapital.com">Anamcara</a>, <a href="https://www.hedosophia.com">Hedosophia</a>, <a href="https://visionaries.vc">Visionaries Club</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Team: </strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/cedrikhoffmann/">Cedrik Hoffmann</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/craig-massie/">Craig Massie</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Signal: </strong>Ameba added 3 people to its team of 8 in the last 90 days before raising a $7M seed round led by Hedosophia</p></li></ul><h4><strong><a href="https://www.finnyai.com">FINNY</a> üá∫üá∏</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Industry: </strong>Sales Enablement</p></li><li><p><strong>What they do: </strong>FINNY AI provides a prospecting tool for wealth managers, utilizing proprietary databases and predictive scoring to personalize prospect recommendations and automate targeted outreach messages. The platform's advanced technology optimizes prospect engagement and streamlines the identification of high-priority prospects.</p></li><li><p><strong>Last Funding:</strong> Pre-Seed</p></li><li><p><strong>Total Funding:</strong> 500‚Äô000 USD</p></li><li><p><strong>Notable Investors: </strong><a href="https://www.ycombinator.com">Y Combinator</a>, <a href="https://www.crossbeam.vc">Crossbeam Venture Partners</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Team: </strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/edenovadia/">Eden Ovadia</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/victoria-toli/">Victoria Toli</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/theodore-janson/">Theodore Janson</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Signal: </strong>Finny has rapidly expanded its team in the fall and is seeing solid growth in website visitors and social media following</p></li></ul><div><hr></div><h2>Growth Startups üöÄ</h2><h4><strong><a href="https://www.legalfly.ai">LEGALFLY</a> üá¨üáß</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Industry:</strong> LegalTech</p></li><li><p><strong>What they do:</strong> LegalFly offers a secure AI platform for legal teams, specializing in contract review, drafting, and discovery, leveraging AI technology to streamline document analysis and reduce review time while prioritizing privacy and security through anonymization. The platform also allows for the creation of specialized Legal AI copilots for training and analysis of unstructured documents.</p></li><li><p><strong>Last Funding:</strong> Series A</p></li><li><p><strong>Total Funding: </strong>18‚Äô560‚Äô508 USD</p></li><li><p><strong>Notable Investors:</strong> <a href="https://www.notion.vc">Notion Capital</a>, <a href="http://redalpine">redalpine</a>, <a href="https://www.fortinocapital.com">Fortino Capital</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mghissassi/">Mehdi Ghissassi</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Team: </strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dennis-montegnies-42b58926/">Dennis Montegnies</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rmiessen/">Ruben Miessen</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Signal: </strong>Legalfly added 11 people in the last 90 days and is hiring for 20 positions, LinkedIn followers more than doubled over the last 6 months</p></li></ul><h4><strong><a href="https://www.attotude.com">Atto Tude</a> üá∫üá∏</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Industry: </strong>Data Centers</p></li><li><p><strong>What they do: </strong>AttoTude specializes in interconnect technology aimed at enhancing data center efficiency, particularly for artificial intelligence and supercomputing applications. This technology addresses networking limitations and facilitates high-speed parallel processing.</p></li><li><p><strong>Last Funding: </strong>Series A</p></li><li><p><strong>Total Funding:</strong> 40‚Äô168‚Äô034 USD</p></li><li><p><strong>Notable Investors: </strong><a href="https://shv.com">Sutter Hill Ventures</a>, <a href="https://www.canaan.com">Canaan</a>, <a href="https://www.wing.vc">Wing Venture Capital</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Team:</strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ianswanson/"> </a><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dave-welch-b359b630/">Dave Welch</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Signal: </strong>After a series-A led by Sutter Hill and Wing, AttoTude has money to spend, with funding per employee standing at $6.69M</p></li></ul><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4