eep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F865edf88-b011-40cc-a46a-12333b9d4402_502x750.jpeg" width="268" height="400.398406374502" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/865edf88-b011-40cc-a46a-12333b9d4402_502x750.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:750,&quot;width&quot;:502,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:268,&quot;bytes&quot;:24435,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F865edf88-b011-40cc-a46a-12333b9d4402_502x750.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F865edf88-b011-40cc-a46a-12333b9d4402_502x750.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F865edf88-b011-40cc-a46a-12333b9d4402_502x750.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F865edf88-b011-40cc-a46a-12333b9d4402_502x750.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Twinsbet besivadinanƒçioje arenoje dar nebuvau buvus. Prabƒógom pastebƒójau kiek atnaujintƒÖ interjero dizainƒÖ, bet garsu, girdƒójau, daug kas skundƒósi. Man, pigiausi≈≥ biliet≈≥ kampe, viskas girdƒójosi normaliai.</p><p>ƒÆdomu, kad organizatoriai vengia ≈æod≈æio ‚Äûmiuziklas‚Äú ‚Äì ≈°ƒØkart tai muzikinƒó drama. Gal miuziklas skamba per linksmai, nors, pvz., ‚Äû≈Ωygimanto Augusto ir Barboros Radvilaitƒós legenda‚Äú bei ‚ÄûLituanica‚Äú vadinti miuziklais. Muzikinƒó drama lyg ir akcentuot≈≥ teatro aspektƒÖ, taƒçiau ≈°iuo atveju tikrai nevertƒójo to daryti, nes puiki muzika nustelbia visas vaidybas ir K. Jak≈°to re≈æis≈´rƒÖ. Skelbiama, kad muzikƒÖ ra≈°ƒó net 4 kompozitoriai, kas savaime tai nieko gero. Vis dƒólto J. Jasinskio (ar beb≈´na Lietuvoje muzikini≈≥ projekt≈≥, nepaliest≈≥ Jievaro rankos?), J. Jurk≈´no, G. Venislovo ir R. Svilainio k≈´rybinis rezultatas tikrai stebinantis ir jaudinantis. Muzika mainosi tarp d≈æiazi≈°kos, klasi≈°kos, rokooperi≈°kos, antanƒóli≈°kos, o orkestro ≈°erdimi tampa kanklƒós.</p><p>Kadangi ≈°io projekto sumanytojai ‚Äì choro, ≈°okio ir orkestro ansamblis ‚ÄûLietuva‚Äú, tai nenuostabu, kad masuotƒó ƒçia grie≈æia pirmu smuiku. Vos pora atskir≈≥ arij≈≥ ƒØsp≈´dingumu galƒójo prilygti choriniams numeriams. Ansamblis atidirbo i≈° peties ir judesiu, ir balsais, ir asistavimu solistams.</p><p>Monika Liu, mano manymu, yra tobulas pasirinkimas ≈°iam vaidmeniui. Gaila, kad re≈æis≈´ri≈°kai ir muzikaliai ji buvo labai menka i≈°naudota. Daugiausia tiesiog vaik≈°ƒçiojo po scenƒÖ su savo juodais ilgaauliais ir atlo≈°tais peƒçiais. Monikos man ypaƒç pritr≈´ko tragi≈°koje pabaigoje (spoiler alert!), kuri vƒólgi re≈æisieriaus liko nei≈°sprƒôsta, tiesiog beprasmi≈°kai nukirsta, kaip kad beprasmi≈°kai nutr≈´ko paƒçios Pliaterytƒós (25-eri≈≥) gyvenimas. Bet argi beprasmi≈°kai? Kur jauno ≈æmogaus drƒÖsos ir aukos apmƒÖstymas? Kitus prikƒólusi i≈° kap≈≥, Emilija mir≈°ta ir negauna net pomirtinƒós arijos u≈ætraukt, kuri buvo suteikta jos motinai.</p><p>Apie motinƒÖ (operos solistƒó Ilona Pliavgo) ‚Äì atskira kalba. Pagal vaidmen≈≥ ry≈°kumƒÖ ir arij≈≥ ƒØsp≈´dingumƒÖ miuziklas galƒójo vadintis ‚ÄûMotina‚Äú, o ne ‚ÄûEmilija‚Äú. Atrodo, kad re≈æisieriui taip patiko nagrinƒóti ƒØtemptus motinos santykius su dukra, ir dukros protestƒÖ prie≈° besiper≈°antƒØ rus≈≥ generolƒÖ (puikus Tadas Girininkas), kad paskui nebeliko laiko sukilimui vaizduoti. Siu≈æeti≈°kai paakcentuota, kad Emilija karo ≈æygi≈≥ ƒómƒósi i≈° esmƒós dƒól to, kad liko na≈°laitƒó, o tokia mintis ka≈ækaip neƒØkvepia. Jei jau trumpam epizodui buvo ƒØtrauktas visada pritrenkiantis Vaidas Bartu≈°as (Kunigas), tai gal juo ir vertƒójo u≈æbaigti ‚Äì Dievas ir Tƒóvynƒó, ar ka≈ækaip pana≈°iai. Pati sau susigalvojau i≈° k≈´rinio logikos i≈°plaukusƒØ moralƒÖ, kad moterims visgi kare ne vieta - abi merginos mir≈°ta/≈æ≈´sta, o pusbrolis Cezaris (Mantas Zemleckas) i≈°gyvena iki 1869 m.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg" width="370" height="355.5083333333333" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1153,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:370,&quot;bytes&quot;:462040,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffc1c200b-92f0-4801-83fb-20b6bd79b163_1200x1153.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Silpniausia muzikinƒós dramos grandis man pasirodƒó libretas (aut. Sandra Bernotaitƒó), kurio tiesmukumas kontrastavo su vaizdinga muzika. Nors vienas ry≈°kesni≈≥ persona≈æ≈≥ buvo Poetas (Andrius Kaniava), taƒçiau paradoksaliai net ir tai negarantavo jokios poetinƒós kalbos. Vos pora ƒØsimintin≈≥ motyv≈≥ ‚Äì u≈æuod≈æiu ≈ævƒórƒØ (apie rusus), pasƒójom vƒójƒÖ, artƒója audra. O visa kita ‚Äì ‚ÄûkƒÖ matau, tƒÖ dainuoju‚Äú ir triviali jausm≈≥ rai≈°ka. Ai≈°ku, nesinori lyginti su galvoje skambƒójusio Gedos genijum, bet juk Lietuva ‚Äì poet≈≥ kra≈°tas, jei kƒÖ ir mokam, tai metaforom kalbƒót. Beje, humoro spektaklyje irgi beveik nƒóra, galƒójo Poetas u≈æmesti juodƒÖ bajeriukƒÖ apie viltis nebeilgai kentƒóti rus≈≥ gniau≈ætus (veiksmas vyksta 1831 m.). Visgi carinƒô kult≈´rƒÖ simbolizavusios balerinos bent man pasirodƒó sƒókmingas humoristinis inkliuzas.</p><p>Minimalistinƒó pilka stumdoma scenografija, juodai balta apranga pasiteisino. Nuleid≈æiami/pakeliami nedideli ekranai, fragmentuojantys heroj≈≥ veidus ir vizualizacijas, taip pat pasiteisino. Tik paƒçios vizulkƒós neretai atrodƒó kiƒçinƒós (piev≈≥ ≈æolƒó; tiesiai ƒØ mus va≈æiuojanti AI sugeneruota patranka), kiek geriau atrodƒó dvar≈≥ griuvƒósiai, o geriausiai ‚Äì tiesiog minimalus dvaro interjeras.</p><div class="poll-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;id&quot;:228385}" data-component-name="PollToDOM"></div><p><em>(Para≈°ykit komentaruose, jei turit kitƒÖ gerƒÖ idƒójƒÖ.)</em></p><p>Tiek ƒçia prikritikavau, bet noriu paraginti ‚ÄûEmilijƒÖ‚Äú pamatyti (artimiausiƒÖ mƒónesƒØ bus rodoma kituose miestuose). Prognozuojam sƒókmƒô Lenkijoj, Latvijoj, gal ir dar kur ex-LDK. ƒÆkvƒópta grƒØ≈æusi i≈°kart nusipirkau bilietus ƒØ 10metƒØ ≈°venƒçiantƒØ, dar nematytƒÖ ‚Äû≈ΩygimantƒÖ ir BarborƒÖ‚Äú. Miuziklas savaime labai ƒØtraukiantis ≈æanras, yra ƒØ kƒÖ pa≈æi≈´rƒóti ir ko paklausyti. Net ir ≈°irdƒØ pavirpina, ypaƒç kai pabaigoje ekranuose pasirodo tikroji Emilija i≈° Pliateri≈≥ giminƒós.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff801c2d7-a677-4e23-a6f4-242701a8e810_740x929.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff801c2d7-a677-4e23-a6f4-242701a8e810_740x929.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff801c2d7-a677-4e23-a6f4-242701a8e810_740x929.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff801c2d7-a677-4e23-a6f4-242701a8e810_740x929.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff801c2d7-a677-4e23-a6f4-242701a8e810_740x929.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fima