 x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><div><hr></div><blockquote><h4>JAV rinkimai</h4></blockquote><p>Ne≈æinau, ar kƒÖ nors JAV rinkimuose lemia ƒØ≈æymybi≈≥ parama kandidatams. Visgi JAV prezidentai ir kandidatai mƒógsta savo galiƒÖ pabrƒó≈æti per muzikƒÖ. Turb≈´t ƒØsimintiniausias praƒójusios savaitƒós video ‚Äì Obama, repuojantis ‚ÄûLose Yourself‚Äú po Eminemo pristatymo Detroite. Obama tikrai liks muzikos istorijoj dƒól ƒØsp≈´dingos inauguracijos su Beyonce ir kit≈≥ bali≈≥ su vis≈≥ mylimiausiais muzikantais. O taip pat ir dƒól nuostabi≈≥ Spotify grojara≈°ƒçi≈≥, kuriuose galimai jo mƒógstamiausios met≈≥ dainos.</p><div id="youtube2-sP2RRwaCPSE" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;sP2RRwaCPSE&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/sP2RRwaCPSE?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p><strong>Kamala Harris</strong>. KamalƒÖ skubƒójo paremti visi, kas netingƒójo (nes per antrƒÖ Bideno kadencijƒÖ muzikantai buvo gerokai aptilƒô). Jos palaikytoj≈≥ sƒÖra≈°e: Eminemas, Bruce Springsteenas, Taylor Swift, Beyonc√© (pirmam kampanijos video panaudota jos daina ‚ÄûFreedom‚Äú), Billie Eilish ir Finneas (<em>We are voting for Kamala Harris and Tim Walz, because they are fighting to protect our reproductive freedom, our planet and our democracy.</em>), Katy Perry, Lil Nas X, Ariana Grande, Lizzo, Megan Thee Stallion, Barbra Streisand, Bon Jovi, Bon Iver, Cardi B (palaikƒó Harris before it was cool), Moby, Neil Young, Pink, Stevie Wonder, Charli XCX (jos albumo pavadinimas ‚ÄûBrat‚Äú virto prezidentiniu ≈°≈´kiu ‚ÄûKamala is brat‚Äú; atlikƒója yra sakiusi, kad brat rei≈°kia ≈æmog≈≥, kuris <em>might have a pack of cigs, a Bic lighter and a strappy white top with no bra</em>).</p><p>Galiausiai, po to, kai Foo Fighters daina ‚ÄûMy Hero‚Äú buvo nelegaliai panaudota Trumpo kampanijoje, grupƒó pasipiktinusi parei≈°kƒó, kad atlygƒØ u≈æ dainos panaudojimƒÖ skirs Kamalos kampanijai.</p><p><strong>Donaldas Trumpas</strong>. Joe Roganas kƒÖ tik pasirod≈æiusiam interviu stebƒójosi, kad Donaldas buvo toks mylimas ≈°ou biznio atstov≈≥ (tarkim, Oprah), kol nepaskelbƒó kandidatuosiantis ƒØ prezidentus. Dabar jo muzikinis antura≈æas labiau nei apgailƒótinas: Kid Rock, country dainininkas Jason Aldean, Billy Ray Cyrus (nors dukra Miley Trumpo nekenƒçia). Ai≈°ku, Kanye West-Ye. Azealia Banks savo paramƒÖ ai≈°kino taip: <em>He‚Äôs just fucking funnyyy. He‚Äôs been through how many bankruptcies? How many wives? How many television shows? Seriously, nothing can take him down</em>. Kodak Black argumentai: <em>I fuck with that boy. And that boy, like, he be vibin‚Äô out here too</em>. Lil Pump u≈æbaigƒó: <em>Greatest president of all time</em>. ≈†itoj kompanijoj gal kiek keisƒçiau atrodo M.I.A., kuri mƒógsta pasisakyti visais politiniais klausimais, be to, yra sakiusi, kad mieliau mirs, nei skiepysis nuo kovido. ≈†iemet ji i≈°rei≈°kƒó paramƒÖ Trumpui.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png" width="320" height="401.423487544484" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:705,&quot;width&quot;:562,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:320,&quot;bytes&quot;:834834,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F162b4838-8b06-41ed-9399-970e14b90ef3_562x705.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Su biƒçiuliu Lil Pump a.k.a. Ma≈æuoju Pumpƒójum</figcaption></figure></div><div><hr></div><blockquote><h4>Nauji albumai</h4></blockquote><div class="image-gallery-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;gallery&quot;:{&quot;images&quot;:[{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c54d2f91-c95f-45ea-b5cb-04a6f65395eb_708x720.png&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e67a5dfc-f15e-4812-bf54-4530d23a4e53_1200x1200.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c9b80605-c49d-4031-9bcc-55418ca6cd41_626x622.png&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/eef4f428-839f-4cad-a4f2-2944f15e7d61_715x712.png&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/004ff064-c3ca-4beb-90b6-76420e5c15f6_1200x1200.jpeg&quot;},{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/55f842f3-694f-4df0-825d-c92d264ad5a7_715x715.png&quot;}],&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;staticGalleryImage&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1d7ccce4-a8a5-4382-a939-0836b80a978a_1456x964.png&quot;}},&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true}"></div><p><strong>(VI) AMBER STREET ‚Äì ‚ÄûOksimoronas‚Äú</strong></p><iframe class="spotify-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab67616d0000b273b8eaa58c69a567f0fb8c306f&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Oksimoronas&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Amber Street&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Album&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/album/0rbIf2npZ8An4CA0Off4Ja&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/0rbIf2npZ8An4CA0Off4Ja" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" loading="lazy" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>Visi≈°kai atsitiktinis atradimas. Klaipƒódieƒçi≈≥ grupƒós debiutinis EP. Patiko shoegazinis jovalas, merginos vokalas ir daina ‚ÄûThy Lazy Peasant‚Äú.</p><p><strong>(V) Veirr ‚Äì ‚ÄûFractured‚Äú</strong></p><div id="youtube2-rFlgXPE9LmA" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;rFlgXPE9LmA&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:&quot;79s&quot;,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/rFlgXPE9LmA?start=79s&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>Nors klipo k≈´rinys ne i≈° naujojo albumo, rekomenduoju pa≈æi≈´rƒóti ‚Äì puikus ≈°iurpus darbas. Trijulƒó VEIRR anksƒçiau vadinosi Pindrops. Muzikoje jie jungia sunk≈≥ industrinƒØ roko skambesƒØ su grubia techn≈´≈°ke. AlbumƒÖ prodiusavo Andrius Kauklys i≈° Happyendless, kas u≈ædeda kokybƒós ≈°tampƒÖ. ‚ÄûOre‚Äú yra <a href="https://www.ore.lt/2023/03/veirr-paleidzia-savo-industrini-virusa?fbclid=IwY2xjawF3KGtleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHfiTI57mZqiFaekONleHaOB2IK-MFOu0YaD2KDOEWeUIQU1fdufUepfl_A_aem_Y1FPD0TtHIV2ExzqS8TORw">publikavƒô pokalbƒØ</a>, kuriame atsiskleid≈æia rimtas grupƒós po≈æi≈´ris ƒØ darbƒÖ.</p><div class="bandcamp-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://veirr.bandcamp.com/album/fractured-2&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Fractured, by Veirr&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;8 track album&quot;,&quot;thumbnail_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9a16506c-643b-4650-a340-54cc667042d3_700x700.jpeg&quot;,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;Veirr&quot;,&quot;embed_url&quot;:&quot;https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=1268948039/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/&quot;,&quot;is_album&quot;:true}" data-component-name="BandcampToDOM"><iframe src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album=1268948039/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=333333/artwork=small/transparent=true/" frameborder="0" gesture="media" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div><p><strong>(IV) dominykas niaura ‚Äì ‚Äûbevietystƒó‚Äú</strong></p><div class="soundcloud-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://api.soundcloud.com/playlists/1895793743&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;bevietystƒó by dominykas niaura&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;\\&quot;bevietystƒó\\&quot; (\\&quot;placelessness\\&quot;) tells a bittersweet docu-fictional story through field recordings, ambient, dub, electronic, and other musical experiments.\\n\\nConceived in 2019, each track is dedicated to a different person, exploring the human condition via themes of mortality, the search for meaning, loneliness, loss, and more.\\n\\nThe result is a deeply atmospheric piece that plays with the tension between memory, imagination, and the passage of time.\\n\\nTracklist:\\n\\n1. i'd still like to walk the streets of my youth\\n2. last night i dreamt that someone loves me\\n3. see you in a better world\\n4. place-less-ness (the irony of fate or after death)\\n5. i lie awake and wish you ill\\n6. i was looking for her bad side like that would bring us closer\\n7. (resignation) everyone's fucked, but not everyone knows it\\n8. don't know how to be happy when it's time to be happy\\n9. why'd i leave you walk alone up there\\n\\nMixed &amp; mastered by Electron Transition\\nReleased by Electron Emitter (EEM073)&quot;,&quot;thumbnail_url&quot;:&quot;https://i1.sndcdn.com/artworks-A0d8zsDmSRmRyLw4-doat8g-t500x500.jpg&quot;,&quot;author_name&quot;:&quot;dominykas niaura&quot;,&quot;author_url&quot;:&quot;https://soundcloud.com/niaura&quot;,&quot;targetUrl&quot;:&quot;https://soundcloud.com/niaura/sets/bevietyste&quot;}" data-component-name="SoundcloudToDOM"><iframe src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?auto_play=false&amp;buying=false&amp;liking=false&amp;download=false&amp;sharing=false&amp;show_artwork=true&amp;show_comments=false&amp;show_playcount=false&amp;show_user=true&amp;hide_related=true&amp;visual=false&amp;start_track=0&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fapi.soundcloud.com%2Fplaylists%2F1895793743" frameborder="0" gesture="media" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div><p>DominykƒÖ esu ƒØsidƒómƒójusi senokai, nuo depresyvios eksperimentikos projekto Suicideoscope ir k≈´rinio <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zbMvtGHU6L4&amp;ab_channel=Suicideoscope">‚ÄûUntuck‚Äú</a>, kurio klipo neberandu youtube (kodƒól?!). O ‚Äûbevietystƒó‚Äú ‚Äì filosofi≈°kas k≈´rinys i≈° lauko ƒØra≈°≈≥, bals≈≥, ambiento, elektronikos, vienatvƒós ir pavadinim≈≥ pamƒÖstymui (‚ÄûnaktƒØ guliu ir tau negero linkiu‚Äú, ‚Äûie≈°kojau jos blogosios pusƒós, lyg taip mes suartƒótume‚Äú). </p><p><strong>(III) ADAS ‚Äì ‚ÄûPlayground‚Äú</strong></p><div class="bandcamp-wrap album" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&qu