m%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F50a0c7f0-981c-4616-ac2a-ae66596bac40_942x1058.heic 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F50a0c7f0-981c-4616-ac2a-ae66596bac40_942x1058.heic 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Su nuliniu biud≈æetu daraus ≈æmones laimingais</figcaption></figure></div><p></p><p>***</p><p>‚Äì Ir tada tie baltarusiai man sako, kam tau ta gimtoji kalba reikalinga. Juk Lietuva ma≈æa. Nepsimoka jos mokintis. Ir, ≈æinot, Domai, a≈° nesubƒójau ƒØvardinti, kam man ta gimtoji kalba reikalinga.<br>‚Äì Na, a≈° galƒóƒçiau jums dabar kokƒØ 20 punkt≈≥ i≈°vardinti, kƒÖ man duoda gimtoji kalba.<br>‚Äì O a≈° negaliu. </p><p>***</p><p>Atrodo ≈°neku su profesionalu, besidrabstanƒçiu apie bera≈°ƒçius lietuvius ir kaip ƒçia viskas blogai. Sakau:<br>‚Äì Mane vis priblo≈°kia kuomet ≈æmogus sako, kad saugo Lietuvi≈≥ kalbƒÖ, bet kai jo papra≈°au i≈°vardinti bent de≈°imt lietuvi≈°k≈≥ knyg≈≥, para≈°yt≈≥ per pastaruosiu penkis metus, jis nesugeba i≈°vardinti.<br>‚Äì A≈° irgi nei≈°vardinƒçiau. Darbe daug skaitau. Lietuvi≈°koms knygoms nelieka laiko.</p><p>≈†iaip tik dar kartƒÖ ƒØsitikinau, kad ne daug tr≈´ko, jog ƒØ kokƒØ mano argumentƒÖ b≈´t≈≥ pasakytƒÖ ‚ÄûkƒÖ tas ≈ævairys ƒçia supranta‚Äú. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic" width="968" height="968" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:968,&quot;width&quot;:968,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:82274,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/heic&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F032a6c3b-b559-4db9-8f09-1b6c34e8e110_968x968.heic 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Su nuliniu biud≈æetu skatinu nepamir≈°ti aktualij≈≥</figcaption></figure></div><p>O mano ataskaitos pagrindinƒó mintis, kuriƒÖ norƒójau perduoti:</p><p>Kalbos mokslas kaip ir bet kuris kitas mokslas nƒóra demokratija. Ne balsavimo b≈´d≈≥ mokslininkai sprend≈æia, kuris teiginys teisingas. Ir jeigu mokslininkƒós(ai) klydo praeityje, nerei≈°kia, kad jie/jos melavo. Tai rei≈°kia, kad mokslas pasimokƒó i≈° klaidos ir ≈æengƒó ≈æingsnƒØ pirmyn.</p><p>Dar kartƒÖ dƒókoju ≈™lai, Airai, Gabijai u≈æ galimybƒô b≈´ti to dalimi. Mano si≈´lymas, jei dar turƒósite jƒóg≈≥ pana≈°iai avanti≈´rai. Prie≈° kviesdami diskusijos dalyvius paklauskite klausim≈≥:<br>Ar VLKK reikalinga?<br>Ar lietuvi≈≥ kalbos ƒØstatymƒÖ reikia panaikinti?</p><p>Jei gaunate du teigiamus atsakymus, to ≈æmogaus diskutuoti nekvieskite. Tokie ≈æmonƒós yra diskusij≈≥ roto virusai.<br>Bent jau man atrodo, kad pasibaigƒô rinkimai kalbos mokslui nieko gero ne≈æada. Apie kalbƒÖ nesuprantantys kalbininkai dar galƒós keturis metus siautƒóti, kalbos ƒØstatymo niekas nelies.</p><p>Vienintelis b≈´das tiesiog juos ignoruoti tiek VLKK, tiek kalbos inspekcijos pastabas. Gimtoji kalba yra prigimtinƒó teisƒó. Jei norite gerai ra≈°yti ‚Äì skaitykite.</p><p>O ≈°iaip tiesiog linkiu pasimƒógauti gera literat≈´ra:<br>Kotryna Zylƒó ‚Äì Mylimi Kaulai;<br>Ur≈°ulƒó Toleikytƒó ‚Äì ≈†uo Vaiduoklis;<br>Ar ≈†lapimas vaistas (leidykla Vytis 1993 m.);<br>Undinƒó Radzeviƒçi≈´tƒó ‚Äì ≈Ωuvys ir drakonai;<br><br>I≈° verstini≈≥, mano aplinkoje dabar siautƒója ir liepƒó man perskaityti: <br>Ayn Rand ‚Äì ≈†altinis.</p><p>Pats laukiu laiko perskaityti, nes labai ƒØdomu kaip pavyko i≈°versti Cormac McCarthy ‚Äì Kraujo meridianas.<br>Ai≈°ku, jei norit daugiau tiesiog u≈æsukite ƒØ knygynƒÖ Eureka. Jei nerasite knyg≈≥, tai bent galƒósite nusifotografuoti ant sofos kur sukrautos knygos. Reklamos knygoms niekada nebus per daug.</p><p></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff41bbafa-519a-4a63-9506-1e7dc0d242ac_920x1154.heic" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff41bbafa-519a-4a63-9506-1e7dc0d242ac_920x1154.heic 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.co