Capital<br><strong>When: </strong>üìÖ Tue, October 8 | 11:00 AM - 1:00 PM CET | Online</p><p>Join us for an in-depth session on Venture Debt tailored specifically for GPs. We will provide a comprehensive overview of venture debt, its structure, and its strategic advantages and drawbacks, focusing on how GPs can leverage these insights for better investment decisions.</p><p>‚ÄãThis masterclass will cover essential aspects of venture debt, from its origins and rationale to detailed explorations of deal terms and geographic variations. Designed with GPs in mind, we will offer practical insights and strategies to enhance your understanding and application of venture debt in your portfolio management.</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://lu.ma/venture-debt&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Join the masterclass here&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;button-wrapper&quot;}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary button-wrapper" href="https://lu.ma/venture-debt"><span>Join the masterclass here</span></a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progr