ano, Italy</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/culttech24">culttech summit</a></strong> | üìÜ 5-6 November | Vienna, Austria</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/GoWest25">GoWest</a> </strong>| üìÜ 28 - 30 January 2025 | üåç Gothenburg, Sweden</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/GITEXEU25">GITEX Europe 2025</a></strong> | üìÜ 23 - 25 May 2025 | üåç Berlin, Germany</p></body></html>	Swiss-based venture capital firm focuses on climate tech investments across North America, Europe, and APAC. The firm manages around ‚Ç¨700M in assets and offers a unique approach to venture capital.	2024-10-03 06:31:04	2024-10-14 08:23:31.399	2024-10-14 09:20:44.198	{vc,climate}	https://api.substack.com/feed/podcast/149467727/cecf4db93f61b96418a56a5f415efa6f.mp3	anon	emerald-vcs-gina-domanig-on-cvc
158	https://www.eu.vc/p/cambridge-scientists-secure-5m-from	Cambridge scientists secure $5M from leading global venture capital funds and corporations to transform scope 3 decarbonization	by Michael Smith, General Partner of Regeneration.VC.	<html><head></head><body><p>Guest post by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ponvalley/">Michael Smith</a>, General Partner of <a href="http://regeneration.vc/">Regeneration.VC</a>.</p><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg" width="1456" height="969" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:969,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:14380611,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb03faed2-2170-4c70-b906-1d60be17fe20_5988x3984.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><a href="http://regeneration.vc/">Regeneration.VC</a>&nbsp;leads&nbsp;Neutreeno‚Äôs&nbsp;Seed&nbsp;round alongside Remarkable Ventures Climate Fund&nbsp;(RVC), Closed Loop Partners, Prequel Ventures, Scania&nbsp;Invest&nbsp;and Beacon Venture Capital.</p><p>CAMBRIDGE, UK,&nbsp;Oct. 3, 2024&nbsp;‚Äì&nbsp;<a href="http://www.neutreeno.com/">Neutreeno</a>, a pioneering deep tech startup&nbsp;spinning out of the University of Cambridge has secured a $5 million Seed round with support from a global syndicate of mission-aligned investors.&nbsp;</p><p>On average,&nbsp;companies&nbsp;have&nbsp;over&nbsp;90%&nbsp;of&nbsp;emissions&nbsp;in&nbsp;their value chain (Scope3),&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://newsroom.accenture.com/news/2022/nearly-all-companies-will-miss-net-zero-goals-without-at-least-doubling-rate-of-carbon-emissions-reductions-by-2030-accenture-report-finds">93% will fail to achieve&nbsp;their&nbsp;net zero goals</a>&nbsp;unless they&nbsp;double the pace of emissions reduction by 2030.&nbsp;This is challenging due to&nbsp;a&nbsp;lack of primary value chain data, the inability to influence suppliers and the high cost of decarbonization.</p><p>Neutreeno‚Äôs proprietary process&nbsp;networks, based on mass and energy flow research,&nbsp;significantly&nbsp;minimise&nbsp;the&nbsp;primary&nbsp;databurden&nbsp;on suppliers&nbsp;and&nbsp;allows&nbsp;enterprises&nbsp;to&nbsp;map&nbsp;product lines faster&nbsp;and with greater&nbsp;precision&nbsp;than&nbsp;existing tools.&nbsp;Their&nbsp;easy-to-use&nbsp;and affordable&nbsp;digital system&nbsp;automatically&nbsp;pinpoints solutions that reduce&nbsp;emissions and costs&nbsp;across 1,000s of suppliers.&nbsp;Neutreeno‚Äôs customers span&nbsp;Europe,&nbsp;North America and Asia,&nbsp;including&nbsp;S&amp;P 500 and FTSE&nbsp;250&nbsp;companies&nbsp;across&nbsp;multiple&nbsp;industries,&nbsp;and&nbsp;a wide range of SMEs.</p><p>Fredrik&nbsp;Nilz√©n, Head of Sustainability at Scania Group,&nbsp;one of&nbsp;Europe‚Äôs&nbsp;largest&nbsp;commercial vehicle manufacturers, emphasized:&nbsp;</p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>Neutreeno offers a unique and innovative solution that is crucial for tackling sustainability challenges with improved efficiency and cost-effectiveness at scale. Scania&nbsp;Invest‚Äôs&nbsp;support emphasizes the strategic importance of advancing Neutreeno‚Äôs pioneering technology in the sustainability landscape.</em>‚Äù</p></div><p>Dr Spencer Brennan,&nbsp;Neutreeno‚Äôs founder,&nbsp;assembled a&nbsp;team&nbsp;of scientists&nbsp;who over&nbsp;two decades&nbsp;pioneered concepts of circularity and resource efficiency&nbsp;in complex&nbsp;supply chains, informing international climate policy.&nbsp;Spencer&nbsp;remarked:&nbsp;</p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>We&nbsp;take&nbsp;a completely novel,&nbsp;robust&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;approach&nbsp;to&nbsp;challenge&nbsp;the&nbsp;Scope 3 status quo.‚Äù&nbsp;</em></p></div><p>Professor Jonathan Cullen,&nbsp;Head of Climate Science at Neutreeno&nbsp;and&nbsp;Lead Author for the&nbsp;IPCC&nbsp;AR6 Industry Chapter,&nbsp;stated: </p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>Neutreeno breaks away from the noisy&nbsp;landscape of tedious, form-Ô¨Ålling accounting-based&nbsp;carbon&nbsp;software</em>.‚Äù</p></div><p>utreeno delivered&nbsp;groundbreaking&nbsp;results for a multi-billion-dollar enterprise&nbsp;customer, identifying&nbsp;a 35% emissions reduction potential across Scope 3&nbsp;for one of its suppliers&nbsp;and automatically pinpointing&nbsp;actions leading to new product designs, procurement changes, and substantial emissions reductions&nbsp;‚Äî&nbsp;all in just four weeks.</p><p>Markus&nbsp;B√∂rner,&nbsp;General Partner of Prequel Ventures, commented on&nbsp;the company‚Äôs&nbsp;key role in supporting&nbsp;Europe‚Äôs Fit for 55&nbsp;target:&nbsp;</p><div class="pullquote"><p><em>"Decarbonizing supply chains&nbsp;is critical,&nbsp;and&nbsp;with&nbsp;EU regulations like CBAM,&nbsp;it has direct business implications for companies. However,&nbsp;it‚Äôs a formidable challenge. Neutreeno&nbsp;brings cutting-edge&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;manufacturing&nbsp;process expertise,&nbsp;making decarbonization achievable at the product level.&nbsp;This game-changing approach adds&nbsp;immense&nbsp;value to&nbsp;suppliers, recognizing their&nbsp;crucial&nbsp;role in the solution.&nbsp;It&nbsp;aligns perfectly&nbsp;with our mission&nbsp;to empower sustainable supply chains, and we‚Äôre&nbsp;excited about&nbsp;its&nbsp;impact&nbsp;on&nbsp;companies in Europe&nbsp;and beyond."</em></p></div><p>Enthused&nbsp;by the company‚Äôs&nbsp;mission&nbsp;to&nbsp;democratize&nbsp;emissions reductions&nbsp;for&nbsp;millions&nbsp;of&nbsp;businesses,&nbsp;Michael Smith, General Partner of Regeneration,&nbsp;commented: </p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>Neutreeno&nbsp;has the&nbsp;first technical system able to move beyond Scope 3 reporting to systematically&nbsp;decarbonize&nbsp;industry, unlocking the&nbsp;US$130 trillion&nbsp;of&nbsp;capital waiting&nbsp;to fund the low-carbon transition</em>.‚Äù</p></div><p>With its innovative approach and strong industry backing, Neutreeno is&nbsp;poised&nbsp;to&nbsp;make&nbsp;a&nbsp;signiÔ¨Åcant&nbsp;impact&nbsp;on&nbsp;global decarbonization&nbsp;efforts,&nbsp;helping companies achieve their climate goals faster than ever before.</p><p><strong>About&nbsp;Neutreeno</strong></p><blockquote></blockquote><p>Utilizing&nbsp;proprietary process networks and engineering models, Neutreeno&nbsp;identifies&nbsp;and&nbsp;eliminates&nbsp;emissions at source. Neutreeno partners with&nbsp;leading&nbsp;businesses&nbsp;wanting&nbsp;to move beyond carbon accounting and take decisive action&nbsp;to&nbsp;decarbonize&nbsp;Scope 3 emissions.&nbsp;Learn more&nbsp;<a href="https://www.neutreeno.com/">here</a>.</p><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" width="1100" height="220" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:220,&quot;width&quot;:1100,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:60754,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackc