media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Join us for <a href="https://bit.ly/NorthStarGITEX24">Expand North Star in Dubai</a> - the world‚Äôs largest startup and investor connector event.</p><p>Discover the tech and investment opportunities fuelling growth across UAE, MENA, and APMEA regions at Expand North Star, inspired by GITEX GLOBAL, on 13-16 October 2024 at Dubai Harbour.</p><div class="native-video-embed" data-component-name="VideoPlaceholder" data-attrs="{&quot;mediaUploadId&quot;:&quot;3e801237-cc2a-4ba6-a478-da627d832df6&quot;,&quot;duration&quot;:null}"></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png" width="750" height="40" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:40,&quot;width&quot;:750,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2>Origins Fund's Salomon &amp; Blaise on why consumer sector is the underdog in venture capital </h2><div id="youtube2-s0140fa6g64" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;s0140fa6g64&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/s0140fa6g64?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>Today, we welcome the amazing duo <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/saiach/">Salomon Aiach</a>, co-founder &amp; General Partner, and <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/blaise-matuidi-b63029226/">Blaise Matuidi</a>, General Partner from <a href="https://www.origins.fund/">Origins Fund</a>.</p><p>Origins is a new type of venture capital fund backing legendary consumer founders with an unfair advantage from pre-seed to series A. They invest $100k to $500k in consumer tech startups and come with the power of influence of LP‚Äôs community and their 160,000,000 followers.</p><p>We invite you to listen to this discussion below for some inspiring stories; besides the actionable advice, you can have a sneak peek at the below.</p><p><em>Watch it here or add it to your episodes on <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/gb/podcast/euvc/id1544598239">Apple </a>or <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/0WO5adjTSnzxCC3l2sRq1f">Spotify</a> üéß chapters for easy navigation available on the Spotify/Apple episode.</em>‚úçÔ∏è Show notes</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png" width="700" height="40" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:40,&quot;width&quot;:700,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2>‚úçÔ∏è Show notes</h2><p><em>We believe in giving you our guests' thinking directly and unaltered. Therefore, no changes, no AI, no nothing has been done to the following sections.</em></p><h3>Blaise‚Äôs journey as an angel investor.</h3><p>I was 27 years old, and for me, it was super important to think about what I can do after. As an athlete, especially if you are a soccer player when your active years come to an end, you realize your career has to change.</p><p>My father always told me, ¬´<em>You need to prepare yourself!</em>¬ª</p><p>I wanted to do something for my kids and try my best.</p><div><hr></div><h3>Why Blaise became the GP of a venture capital fund.</h3><p>We always start from something, right?</p><p>I started as a business angel, and this is how I got the chance to meet some people, and one of my Partners now at Origin. We felt the desire to bring together both of our worlds, and I realized I can provide added-value to companies through social media, and help companies enhance their communication power. We, now represent an audience of 160M and our athletes are recognized worldwide.</p><p>I sport, I always liked that together we are stronger, and I think there is a huge value in connecting athletes with the business world. </p><div><hr></div><h3>Salomon on discipline and work ethic.</h3><p>The life of an athlete looks glamorous from the outside. You go to a stadium, watch a game, then watch his lifestyle on Instagram, and everything looks glamorous.</p><p>But, it‚Äôs more than that, it‚Äôs about the work ethic those people have and the discipline to be the best. </p><p>For example, when we have a partners meeting at Origin, and Blaise is driving the team to what matters most. Our job is to invest, so if we haven‚Äôt seen new companies in December, we have to focus on that no matter what.</p><p>So, life can look glamorous from the outside, but deep down, it requires a strong work ethic, discipline, and mental resilience to become the best. </p><h3>Salomon on why the consumer sector is the underdog in the VC world.</h3><p>A legendary VC told me that being a consumer investor is the best way to have a short career in the industry.</p><p>Consumer is really hard, and we are aware of that. That‚Äôs why we given the high-profile of our LPs, right now, we, and the entire team has an immense amount of pressure to not only return the money to our LPs, but returning a really high-value. </p><p>The way we structure our portfolio is to ‚Äúderisk‚Äù what consumer means. </p><p>I just looked at a company today, who has crazy numbers in retention. But in the end I am asking myself what is this company gonna look like in 6-months or a year from now? It‚Äôs gonna be just another Clubhouse? It‚Äôs going to be another company in the market?</p><p>I think consumer is very binary, and we‚Äôre building the portfolio by taking a risk on binary bets.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png" width="700" height="40" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:40,&quot;width&quot;:700,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2><strong>Cambridge Scientists Secure $5M from Leading Global Venture Capital Funds and Corporations to Transform Scope 3 Decarbonization</strong></h2><p>Guest post by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ponvalley/">Michael Smith</a>, General Partner of <a href="http://regeneration.vc/">Regeneration.VC</a>.</p><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg" width="1456" height="969" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:969,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:14380611,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc5823fb6-457a-456c-a3c6-8a5b222f53de_5988x3984.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><a href="http://regeneration.vc/">Regeneration.VC</a>&nbsp;leads&nbsp;Neutreeno‚Äôs&nbsp;Seed&nbsp;round alongside Remarkable Ventures Climate Fund&nbsp;(RVC), Closed Loop Partners, Prequel Ventures, Scania&nbsp;Invest,&nbsp;and Beacon Venture Capital.</p><p>CAMBRIDGE, UK,&nbsp;Oct. 3, 2024<a href="http://www.neutreeno.com/">‚ÄîNeutreeno</a>, a pioneering deep tech startup based at the University of Cambridge, has secured a $5 million Seed round with support from a global syndicate of mission-aligned investors.&nbsp;</p><p>On average,&nbsp;companies&nbsp;have&nbsp;over&nbsp;90%&nbsp;of&nbsp;emissions&nbsp;in&nbsp;their value chain (Scope3),&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href="https://newsroom.accenture.com/news/2022/nearly-all-companies-will-miss-net-zero-goals-without-at-least-doubling-rate-of-carbon-emissions-reductions-by-2030-accenture-report-finds">93% will fail to achieve&nbsp;their&nbsp;net zero goals</a>&nbsp;unless they&nbsp;double the pace of emissions reduction by 2030.&nbsp;This is challenging due to&nbsp;a&nbsp;lack of primary value chain data, the inability to influence suppliers, and the high cost of decarbonization.</p><p>Neutreeno‚Äôs proprietary process networks, based on mass and energy flow research, significantly minimize the primary data burden on suppliers and allow enterprises to map product lines faster and with greater precision than existing tools.&nbsp;Their&nbsp;easy-to-use&nbsp;and affordable&nbsp;digital system&nbsp;automatically&nbsp;pinpoints solutions that reduce&nbsp;emissions and costs&nbsp;across 1,000s of suppliers.&nbsp;Neutreeno‚Äôs customers span Europe, North America and Asia, including S&amp;P 500 and FTSE 250 companies across multiple industries and a wide range of SMEs.</p><p>Fredrik&nbsp;Nilz√©n, Head of Sustainability at Scania Group,&nbsp;one of&nbsp;Europe‚Äôs&nbsp;largest&nbsp;commercial vehicle manufacturers, emphasized:&nbsp;</p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>Neutreeno offers a unique and innovative solution that is crucial for tackling sustainability challenges with improved efficiency and cost-effectiveness at scale. Scania&nbsp;Invest‚Äôs&nbsp;support emphasizes the strategic importance of advancing Neutreeno‚Äôs pioneering technology in the sustainability landscape.</em>‚Äù</p></div><p>Dr Spencer Brennan,&nbsp;Neutreeno‚Äôs founder,&nbsp;assembled a&nbsp;team&nbsp;of scientists&nbsp;who over&nbsp;two decades&nbsp;pioneered concepts of circularity and resource efficiency&nbsp;in complex&nbsp;supply chains, informing international climate policy.&nbsp;Spencer&nbsp;remarked:&nbsp;</p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>We&nbsp;take&nbsp;a completely novel,&nbsp;robust&nbsp;engineering&nbsp;approach&nbsp;to&nbsp;challenge&nbsp;the&nbsp;Scope 3 status quo.‚Äù&nbsp;</em></p></div><p>Professor Jonathan Cullen,&nbsp;Head of Climate Science at Neutreeno&nbsp;and&nbsp;Lead Author for the&nbsp;IPCC&nbsp;AR6 Industry Chapter,&nbsp;stated: </p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>Neutreeno breaks away from the noisy&nbsp;landscape of tedious, form-Ô¨Ålling accounting-based&nbsp;carbon&nbsp;software</em>.‚Äù</p></div><p>Neutreeno delivered&nbsp;groundbreaking&nbsp;results for a multi-billion-dollar enterprise&nbsp;customer, identifying&nbsp;a 35% emissions reduction potential across Scope 3&nbsp;for one of its suppliers&nbsp;and automatically pinpointing&nbsp;actions leading to new product designs, procurement changes, and substantial emissions reductions&nbsp;‚Äî&nbsp;all in just four weeks.</p><p>Markus&nbsp;B√∂rner,&nbsp;General Partner of Prequel Ventures, commented on&nbsp;the company‚Äôs&nbsp;key role in supporting&nbsp;Europe‚Äôs Fit for 55&nbsp;target:&nbsp;</p><div class="pullquote"><p><em>"Decarbonizing supply chains&nbsp;is critical,&nbsp;and&nbsp;with&nbsp;EU regulations like CBAM,&nbsp;it has direct business implications for companies. However,&nbsp;it‚Äôs a formidable challenge. Neutreeno&nbsp;brings cutting-edge&nbsp;industrial&nbsp;manufacturing&nbsp;process expertise,&nbsp;making decarbonization achievable at the product level.&nbsp;This game-changing approach adds&nbsp;immense&nbsp;value to&nbsp;suppliers, recognizing their&nbsp;crucial&nbsp;role in the solution.&nbsp;It&nbsp;aligns perfectly&nbsp;with our mission&nbsp;to empower sustainable supply chains, and we‚Äôre&nbsp;excited about&nbsp;its&nbsp;impact&nbsp;on&nbsp;companies in Europe&nbsp;and beyond."</em></p></div><p>Enthused&nbsp;by the company‚Äôs&nbsp;mission&nbsp;to&nbsp;democratize&nbsp;emissions reductions&nbsp;for&nbsp;millions&nbsp;of&nbsp;businesses,&nbsp;Michael Smith, General Partner of Regeneration,&nbsp;commented: </p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚Äú<em>Neutreeno&nbsp;has the&nbsp;first technical system able to move beyond Scope 3 reporting to systematically&nbsp;decarbonize&nbsp;industry, unlocking the&nbsp;US$130 trillion&nbsp;of&nbsp;capital waiting&nbsp;to fund the low-carbon transition</em>.‚Äù</p></div><p>With its innovative approach and strong industry backing, Neutreeno is&nbsp;poised&nbsp;to&nbsp;make&nbsp;a&nbsp;signiÔ¨Åcant&nbsp;impact&nbsp;on&nbsp;global decarbonization&nbsp;efforts,&nbsp;helping companies achieve their climate goals faster than ever before.</p><p><strong>About&nbsp;Neutreeno</strong></p><blockquote></blockquote><p>Utilizing&nbsp;proprietary process networks and engineering models, Neutreeno&nbsp;identifies&nbsp;and&nbsp;eliminates&nbsp;emissions at source. Neutreeno partners with&nbsp;leading&nbsp;businesses&nbsp;wanting&nbsp;to move beyond carbon accounting and take decisive action&nbsp;to&nbsp;decarbonize&nbsp;Scope 3 emissions.&nbsp;Learn more&nbsp;<a href="https://www.neutreeno.com/">here</a>.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F003e6b29-8537-476f-9302-6aec713a7018_1100x220.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F003e6b29-8537-476f-9302-6aec713a7018_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F003e6b29-8537-476f-9302-6aec713a7018_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F003e6b29-8537-476f-9302-6aec713a7018_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F003e6b29-8537-476f-9302-6aec713a7018_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F003e6b29-8537-476f-9302-6aec713a7018_1100x220.png" width="1100" height="220" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/003e6b29-8537-476f-9302-6aec713a7018_1100x220.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:220,&quot;width&q