84e9fb103338_1920x1080.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc21aae73-3a0b-4f50-a20a-84e9fb103338_1920x1080.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc21aae73-3a0b-4f50-a20a-84e9fb103338_1920x1080.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc21aae73-3a0b-4f50-a20a-84e9fb103338_1920x1080.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>The harsh truth is that less than 1% of startups globally are successful in securing VC funding.</p><p>As a first-time tech founder, you‚Äôre no stranger to the highs and lows of bringing an innovative idea to life. While your industry knowledge and passion drive you forward, the reality of needing financial backing to fuel your vision becomes increasingly pressing. </p><p>After bootstrapping with your savings and small investments from supportive friends and family, you‚Äôre ready to enter the world of business angels and venture capitalists (VCs).</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.eu.vc/p/finding-the-right-partner-beyond&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Read the full story here&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Butt