æio), bet smagus, apie draugystƒô, linksmai atskleid≈æiantis dramati≈°kƒÖ temƒÖ ir prapleƒçiantis akiratƒØ. Naujausias mano sƒÖra≈°e, tai dar laiko nepatikrintas.</p><p>13. <strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xUz6y6ANIgE&amp;ab_channel=Spotnick">Control</a> </strong>(2007)</p><p>‚ÄûKontrolƒô‚Äú ≈æi≈´rƒójau kino teatre, buvo labai li≈´dna, net nesinorƒójo paskui giliau pa≈æindintis su Joy Division muzika. Atrodƒó, kad itin estetizuotas juodai baltas vaizdas kontrastavo su itin chaoti≈°ka, tragi≈°ka lemtimi.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafa82b2c-19b3-4da0-9688-946961cf9c7d_1000x563.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafa82b2c-19b3-4da0-9688-946961cf9c7d_1000x563.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafa82b2c-19b3-4da0-9688-946961cf9c7d_1000x563.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafa82b2c-19b3-4da0-9688-946961cf9c7d_1000x563.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fafa82b2c-19b3-4da0-9688-946961cf9c7d_1000x563.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fim