age/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc950a63b-5435-47c8-b2a8-ff0e1729b795_1024x512.png	anon	alt-goes-mainstream-ep-105
154	https://www.eu.vc/p/the-great-vc-reset	The great VC reset	by Alokik Advani, Managing Partner at Fidelity International Strategic Ventures. | Originally published on Fidelity International Strategic Ventures.	<html><head></head><body><p>Guest post by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alokik-advani-019443/">Alokik Advani</a>, Managing Partner at <a href="https://fisv.com/">Fidelity International Strategic Ventures</a>. | Originally published on <a href="https://fisv.com/perspectives/the-great-vc-reset">Fidelity International Strategic Ventures</a>.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png" width="1440" height="829" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:829,&quot;width&quot;:1440,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1436088,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>As we take stock of the fintech landscape in 2024, it's evident that the fervour of 2021's funding frenzy has waned. Buoyed by optimism and a bullish market, the post-pandemic funding heights often set companies up with a comfortable two-or three-year runway. Fast forward to today, and those funds (even if managed conservatively) are nearing exhaustion. A recent report from Morgan Stanley has underscored this reality, indicating that <strong><a href="https://www.ft.com/content/3a6af52a-7eec-434b-bb14-f590b9fef5a7?mod=article_inline">more than 50% of unicorns</a></strong> will need to seek additional capital before the year's end.&nbsp;</p><p>Now, with the pressure mounting to raise new capital, startups face a critical reckoning: what progress has been made since the last funding round? Has their growth rate remained steady or accelerated? Have they met or surpassed their forecasts? And perhaps most importantly, have economic headwinds elongated sales cycles for their products or services? For many, the responses to these lines of inquiry will likely be ‚Äúflat, steady, not met, elongated,‚Äù not exactly the winning ‚ÄòVC Bingo‚Äô card investors seek.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png" width="1456" height="445" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:445,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Median cash runway (in months) by revenue band and start-up category. Source: Morgan Stanley Venture Vision: Cash Burn = M&amp;A.&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Median cash runway (in months) by revenue band and start-up category. Source: Morgan Stanley Venture Vision: Cash Burn = M&amp;A." title="Median cash runway (in months) by revenue band and start-up category. Source: Morgan Stanley Venture Vision: Cash Burn = M&amp;A." srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6434185f-9661-4c82-9df0-9466a68631af_1505x460.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Median cash runway (in months) by revenue band and start-up category. Source: Morgan Stanley Venture Vision: Cash Burn = M&amp;A.</figcaption></figure></div><p>Today's funding environment marks an interesting shift for founders who, during the frenzied pace of 2021, were sought after by every VC under the sun. Now the roles have reversed: investors are increasingly seeking more for less. For startups seeking fresh capital, the road to raising will likely be far longer, tougher, and more competitive than before. As the funding ecosystem faces constraints and runways come to a halt, it is a sad inevitability that many will not raise again, often marking their end.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png" width="1456" height="677" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:677,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Source: Saddling up for the unicorn massacre, Financial Times, October 2023&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="Source: Saddling up for the unicorn massacre, Financial Times, October 2023" title="Source: Saddling up for the unicorn massacre, Financial Times, October 2023" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9237d572-f043-4b23-9e79-3e3bbfca532c_4085x1900.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Source: Saddling up for the unicorn massacre, Financial Times, October 2023</figcaption></figure></div><p>What may be of some comfort amid this gloom is to consider the cyclical nature of what we face today. Reflecting on the dot-com bubble and the post-covid heights of 2021, it‚Äôs hard not to draw comparisons between the two. Through-the-roof valuations, widely unprofitable business models and (often) first-time founders. While the bursting of the dot-com bubble saw the demise of many, this period too saw the emergence of industry behemoths, the likes of Amazon, eBay and Nvidia, that still exist today. Arguably, in times of hardship, only those with excellent product-market fit, a clear route to profitability and an adaptable leadership team can weather the storm. Those who do emerge will have gleaned invaluable lessons, setting them up for enduring success.</p><p>The bursting of a bubble, too, can mark a turning point for the funding ecosystem. With VCs and investors coming away with a heightened sense of prudence, they begin to embrace a more cautious and discerning approach to investment, implementing thorough due diligence processes and a more diversified portfolio. A decline in ‚ÄúVC tourism‚Äù leaves founders better placed to work with investors whose expertise and resources can provide meaningful support and strategic guidance beyond an initial funding injection.</p><p>Growth investors are now laser-focused on discerning a glimmer of hope amid the tunnel of cash burn. With increased scrutiny, founders need to be ready to demonstrate what they have achieved and provide proof and metrics as to how they have reached their inflection point. So, what‚Äôs the road ahead for start-up founders and management teams? Here‚Äôs my advice.</p><h4><strong>Focus on the Fundamentals:</strong></h4><p>Investors have and will shift their focus from speculative hype to fundamentals. We will see increased emphasis on profitability, sustainable growth, and viable business models rather than solely relying on user acquisition and market share. The coveted unicorn status, once a metric that demarcated companies destined for longevity and success, has lost its glitz. Once rare, unicorns are now commonplace, and the susceptibility to being crowned or de-crowned at the whim of investors has seen many argue for other more robust metrics to be used as proxies for success. As <strong><a href="https://techcrunch.com/2022/05/10/the-age-of-the-centaur-100m-arr-is-the-new-cloud-valuation-milestone/">one article highlights</a></strong>, founders need to ditch their unicorn dreams and instead focus on centaur status, ‚Äúreaching the $100 million ARR threshold that connotes having the product, go-to-market and operational competencies to endure.‚Äù</p><h4><strong>Know your product (and your market):</strong></h4><p>Obvious but paramount. For founders raising in the current climate, knowing your customers and how your product meets and solves their needs is key. With shifting consumer behaviour and evolving market dynamics, anecdotes and superstitions are not enough; founders need clear, actionable data to serve as the foundation of roadmaps and explanations as to what and where funds deployed will be spent. A strong grasp of product-market fit informs resource allocation, prioritisation, and iteration decisions, optimising offerings and driving sustainable growth. In essence, founders equipped with this insight not only weather storms but are equally poised and confident to capitalise on emerging opportunities.</p><h4><strong>Don‚Äôt dread the down round:</strong></h4><p>The bursting of the bubble led to a much-needed correction in the market. It brought valuations back to more realistic levels, separating sustainable business models from speculative ventures. This rationalisation laid the foundation for more stable growth in the tech industry. While, with the exception of AI, the ecosystem appears divided into haves and have-nots, the optimal strategy for founders is simple: raise a pragmatic amount of capital that can sustain the business until it achieves cash flow breakeven and beyond. All sounds easy enough until you factor valuations into the equation. Straddling the line between art and science and predicated on growth trajectories and profit margins, pricing is a challenging task for investors and founders alike. However, ensuring each round is priced correctly is a crucial part of the funding cycle.</p><p>Part of this process, is understanding when and why to take a down round. Increasingly, I am seeing puzzling scenarios where founders are pushing to draw a line in the sand from the high watermarks of 2021 and entertain the notion of a down round. Their existing investors, however, staunchly resist, fearing the repercussions on their own performance metrics and subsequent fund raises.</p><p>So why consider taking a cut to a valuation? If priced fairly, a down round offers a silver lining. It not only allows new investors to enter at sensible valuations but also (and arguably more importantly) resets the Employee Stock Ownership Plan (ESOP), ensuring that employees' options aren't rendered worthless, keeping their skin in the game with future wealth incentivization. Instead, the prevailing trend sees companies clinging to lofty valuations, opting instead to take on complex structures like liquidation preferences and minimum return thresholds. This proverbial kicking the can-down-the-road approach is shortsighted and merely postpones the inevitable, delaying the much-needed <strong>reset</strong> that could propel the company forward.</p><p>This isn‚Äôt to say we should encourage markdowns at any cost, and ultimately, any savvy founder wants to keep their investors happy. Flexibility, when occurring on both sides of the table, can foster a more harmonious and ultimately more profitable ecosystem for everyone. As long-term, patient investors, we advocate for a path characterised by clean terms, minimal structure, and transparent, sensibly priced rounds. Such an approach fosters alignment across management teams and investors, paving the way for sustainable growth and meaningful exits.</p><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" width="1100" height="220" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:220,&quot;width&quot;:1100,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:60754,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"><strong>Wanna be featured on eu.vc? Learn how <a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/submit-your-contribution-to-unfiltered">here.</a></strong></figcaption></figure></div></body></html>	The funding frenzy of 2021 has waned, and more than 50% of unicorns will need to seek additional capital before the year's end. Startups face a critical reckoning.	2024-10-04 13:59:50	2024-10-14 08:22:12.334	2024-10-14 08:56:42.083	{vc}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa7625afb-7653-4fe1-a191-e943d774bd15_1440x829.png	anon	the-great-vc
153	https://www.eu.vc/p/the-consumerisation-of-health-part-12f	The Consumerisation of Health (Part 3)	by Estia Ryan, Principal & Head of Research at Eka Ventures. | Originally published on Eka Ventures Newsletter.	<html><head></head><body><p>Guest post by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/estia-ryan/">Estia Ryan</a>, Principal &amp; Head of Research at <a href="https://www.ekavc.com/">Eka Ventures</a>. | Originally published on <a href="https://ekavc.substack.com/p/the-consumerisation-of-health-part-5dc">Eka Ventures Newsletter</a>.</p><div><hr></div><p>This is the final edition of our exploration of the Consumerisation of Health<strong>.</strong> We‚Äôre now diving into OXcan, an Eka portfolio company on the cutting edge of early-stage cancer diagnostics.</p><p>After covering <a href="https://ekavc.substack.com/p/the-consumerisation-of-health-part">Neko Health</a> and <a href="https://ekavc.substack.com/p/the-consumerisation-of-health-part-5dc">Daye</a> in previous weeks, we‚Äôve seen how consumer health companies are tackling everything from general population screening to targeted women‚Äôs health.</p><p>The next leg of Consumer Health sits in high acuity diagnostics, such as early cancer detection. OXcan is redefining early cancer detection, enabling patients to take action earlier and dramatically improving outcomes.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png" width="1456" height="497" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:497,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ed873f4-a802-472b-9a2c-c13e7b6ace26_1839x628.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>*<em>Note that the information in this newsletter is all publicly available.</em></p><div><hr></div><h2>OXcan: Revolutionizing Early Cancer Detection (Part 3) üóûÔ∏è</h2><p>Founded in 2020 by Peter Jianrui Liu and Andreas Halner, OXcan (Oxford Cancer Diagnostics) is transforming how we approach cancer detection. At the core of its mission is a powerful idea: diagnosing cancer as early as possible can drastically improve survival rates.</p><p>But OXcan isn‚Äôt just focused on early detection; they‚Äôre making it accessible, convenient, and affordable to the general population. They leverage a blood test focused on protein detection for early cancer detection combining a state of art proteomics and machine learning platform. These tests are low-invasive and offer earlier detection of lung cancer.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png" width="599" height="350.9251373626374" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:853,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:599,&quot;bytes&quot;:1574421,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ac5ec2c-24ff-403d-be4a-ba40074c867d_1996x1170.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">OXcan website</figcaption></figure></div><h3>The promise of early detection</h3><p>Historically, cancer diagnostics have been reactive, focusing on people who present symptoms and often occurring at the late stage of cancer‚Äôs development. This reactive approach however can lead to late-stage diagnoses when treatment options are limited, and success rates drop drastically. Today, <a href="https://www.cancerresearchuk.org/health-professional/cancer-statistics-for-the-uk">almost half (46%)</a> of all cancers are diagnosed at Stages 3 and 4 in the UK.</p><p>OXcan is flipping this approach. Their vision is rooted in the concept of ‚Äúearly biomarkers‚Äù‚Äîproteins traces in the blood that indicate the presence of cancer long before it‚Äôs detectable by traditional imaging. The WHO estimates that diagnosing cancer at the early stages of its development r<a href="https://www.who.int/news/item/03-02-2017-early-cancer-diagnosis-saves-lives-cuts-treatment-costs">educes costs by 2-4x</a>, compared with late-stage diagnoses.</p><p>Their three pronged approach of (1) cancer expertise, (2) focus on multi-omics, and (3) machine learning enables them to enable curative cancer treatment through early detection.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png" width="1456" height="323" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:323,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:114920,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F80739a06-ccc4-4962-aab5-757752ea6f96_1994x442.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">OXcan website</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Comparing pathways: the traditional vs. OXcan model</h3><p>The current public health pathway for cancer screening is resource-intensive and often delayed. Early stage lung cancer is <a href="https://thorax.bmj.com/content/60/4/268">largely asymptomatic</a> and typically shows few obvious physical changes.</p><p>The <a href="https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/lung-cancer/diagnosis-treatment/drc-20374627">Mayo Clinic</a> mentions that Incumbent tests include:</p><blockquote><p><em><strong>Imaging tests.</strong>&nbsp;Imaging tests make pictures of the body. They can show the location and size of the lung cancer. Tests might include X-ray, MRI, CT,&nbsp;and positron emission tomography, which also is called a&nbsp;scan.</em></p><p><em><strong>Sputum cytology.</strong>&nbsp;Sputum is the mucus that is coughed up from the lungs. If you are coughing up sputum, it can be looked at under a microscope. The sputum can sometimes show lung cancer cells.</em></p><p><em><strong>Biopsy.</strong>&nbsp;A biopsy is a procedure to remove a sample of tissue for testing in a lab.</em></p></blockquote><p>What‚Äôs more, lung cancer wait lists are some of the longest in the UK with 15% of suspected cancer referrals having to wait &gt;104 days for treatment.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png" width="595" height="326.1057692307692" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:798,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:595,&quot;bytes&quot;:518638,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F36c99a44-c473-49a0-afd7-779d878573f9_2390x1310.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"><a href="https://www.cancerresearchuk.org/sites/default/files/performance_measures_across_the_cancer_pathway_0.pdf">Cancer Research</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>The <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cm28el83dxno">BBC published a piece</a> just this week on 6 innovations which could drastically improve the burden on the NHS - and OXcan taps into 2 of these:</p><ol><li><p>Tests &amp; scans in shopping centers <em>(potential OXcan)</em></p></li><li><p>Lung cancer screening trucks (<em>OXcan</em>)</p></li></ol><p>As a result of a cheap, low-invasive, and simple test, OXcan will be able to reach a mass-market of consumers at various touch points in their day.</p><h3>OXcan's innovation: breaking down the science</h3><p>OXcan‚Äôs technology is rooted in liquid biopsy ‚Äî a new approach to cancer diagnostics. More specifically, OXcan is using state of art multi-omic liquid biopsy analysis with a focus on proteomics.</p><p>Unlike traditional biopsies, which require invasive surgical procedures, a liquid biopsy looks for tiny fragments of cancer DNA that shed into the bloodstream. This makes it possible to detect the presence of cancer in its earliest stages without needing a tissue sample.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png" width="575" height="363.3241758241758" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:920,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:575,&quot;bytes&quot;:353596,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42a1a8be-15ae-4190-aa8b-c2ef7ba08d4c_1950x1232.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">OXcan website</figcaption></figure></div><p>OXcan‚Äôs research focuses heavily on machine learning and genomic data. Their algorithms analyze the molecular profile of blood samples, detecting minute changes in DNA that signal the presence of cancerous cells.</p><h3>Diagnostics crash course: sensitivity and specificity</h3><p>When evaluating diagnostic tools, two key metrics are sensitivity and specificity. <strong>Sensitivity</strong> measures how effectively a test identifies true positives, meaning it detects people who actually have a condition. A test with high sensitivity minimizes false negatives, ensuring most cases are caught.</p><p>On the other hand, <strong>specificity</strong> refers to a test‚Äôs ability to identify true negatives‚Äîthose who don‚Äôt have the condition. High specificity reduces false positives, preventing healthy individuals from being mistakenly diagnosed. In the context of vaginal health diagnostics, like Daye‚Äôs microbiome screening, balancing both sensitivity and specificity is crucial to ensuring accurate and actionable results.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png" width="330" height="601" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:601,&quot;width&quot;:330,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:51022,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F79750f07-d47d-41e5-9fe5-36d3c3c0e56e_330x601.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption">Wikipedia</figcaption></figure></div><p>OXcan is delivering very impressive early results on both sensitivity and specificity.</p><h3>Impact and future growth: democratizing cancer care</h3><p>OXcan‚Äôs work fits into a larger trend of consumer-driven healthcare, where individuals have more control and transparency over their health. By empowering patients to monitor their risk before symptoms even appear, OXcan is shifting the paradigm toward a more proactive and preventative model.</p><p>This is particularly important given the strain on public health systems globally. Early detection not only saves lives but also reduces the cost of cancer treatment by avoiding expensive, late-stage interventions.</p><h3>OXcan in the broader consumer health landscape</h3><p>Much like Neko Health and Daye, OXcan represents the next wave of healthcare innovation that centers on consumer empowerment. By placing diagnostics in the hands of individuals, they are breaking down barriers in accessibility and enabling earlier, more effective treatments.</p><div><hr></div><h3>Week in Impact Articles&nbsp;‚úçüèΩ</h3><ul><li><p>Monday: <a href="https://www.edie.net/ed-miliband-pledges-to-reinstate-energy-efficiency-mandate-for-rented-homes/?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=edie_daily_news_alert_24-09-2024&amp;utm_content=edie_daily_news_alert_24-09-2024+CID_f91ddbfbc90c80aca0c05063e89dad50&amp;utm_source=campaign%20monitor&amp;utm_term=Ed%20Miliband%20pledges%20to%20reinstate%20energy%20efficiency%20mandate%20for%20rented%20homes">Ed Miliband pledges to reinstate energy efficiency mandate for rented homes</a></p></li><li><p>Tuesday: <a href="https://heatmap.news/economy/microsoft-three-mile-island-nuclear-constellation?utm_campaign=heatmap_daily_free&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;_hsenc=p2ANqtz--kwvqgJoW7GC9Axp1H5_61XSB1Y4vBtxdHtl9wu2wwtnUHftzVDyQ930H0C6MwvWVNruA0-0YGw0Y7FStypLBlk6d47w&amp;_hsmi=325614142&amp;utm_content=325614142&amp;utm_source=hs_email">Microsoft‚Äôs Mega Deal Is a Massive Victory for Nuclear Power</a></p></li><li><p>Wednesday: <a href="https://techcrunch.com/2024/09/20/health-insurance-startup-alan-reaches-45-billion-valuation-with-new-funding-round/">Health insurance startup Alan reaches $4.5B valuation with new $193M funding round</a></p></li><li><p>Thursday: <a href="https://www.nfx.com/post/verticalization-of-everything">The Verticalization of Everything</a></p></li><li><p>Friday: <a href="https://www.health.org.uk/publications/long-reads/ai-in-health-care-what-do-the-public-and-nhs-staff-think">AI in health care: what do the public and NHS staff think?</a></p></li></ul><div><hr></div><h3>3 Key Charts&nbsp;<strong>üìä</strong></h3><h4>1. Software (growth) in an increasingly AI world.</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f3aafe-806e-4e13-8454-f5f33b9d5ce7_822x562.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f3aafe-806e-4e13-8454-f5f33b9d5ce7_822x562.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f3aafe-806e-4e13-8454-f5f33b9d5ce7_822x562.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f3aafe-806e-4e13-8454-f5f33b9d5ce7_822x562.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12f3aafe-806e-4e13-8454-f5f33b9d5ce7_822x562.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://subst