ng><br>by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/iuliatudor/">Iulia Tudor</a>, Ascension Fund III Partner. | Originally published <a href="https://www.ascension.vc/2024/09/19/our-ai-investing-lens/">Ascension VC</a>.</p><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Ascension VC's AI investment strategy focuses on impact-driven startups that serve lower-income consumers through AI innovations. With portfolio examples like Credit Kudos (exit to Apple) and CourtCorrect, they spotlight AI's potential to improve financial access, legal outcomes, and healthcare. </p><p>Ascension prioritizes startups with proprietary data and sector-specific insights, viewing AI as a tool to reduce social inequalities by lowering costs, improving access, and boosting earnings for underserved groups. This approach blends profit and purpose, aiming for both "impact dragons" and systemic change.</p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/ascension-vcs-ai-investing-lens">Read the article here.</a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700