s distribution and the shift toward wealth channels, highlighting how registered funds (once niche) are driving growth. For investors, this tech shift means greater efficiency in fund administration and post-investment processes, with AI unlocking new value and reducing costs. As private markets embrace tech, it‚Äôs clear: the future of alts is high-tech and investor-friendly.</p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/monthly-alt-pulse-ep-12-taking-the">Listen to the podcast episode here. </a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" wid