re></div><p><strong><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/fighting-a-global-public-health-concern">Fighting a global public health concern with conversational AI</a><br></strong>by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/martinjbryant/">Martin SFP Bryant</a>, Founder of <a href="https://preseednow.com/">PreSeed Now</a>. | Originally published on <a href="https://preseednow.com/p/leaf-ai-lola-cares">PreSeed Now</a>.</p><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Leaf AI‚Äôs "Lola Cares" tackles social isolation among elderly and disabled individuals through an AI-powered digital companion. With Lola, users can have meaningful conversations, which are summarized for caregivers to foster stronger relationships. </p><p>This B2B SaaS solution, especially impactful in dementia care, uses reminiscence therapy and real-time reporting to enhance patient well-being and alleviate caregiver burnout. Leaf AI, part of Edinburgh's AI Accelerator, is a promising entry in healthtech, addressing the WHO-recognized health threat of loneliness‚Äîa compelling sector for VCs in impact and healthcare investments.</p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/fighting-a-global-public-health-concern">Read the article here.</a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a