2919ae35b10_1714x814.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb9f428f9-ea1d-4718-a34f-a2919ae35b10_1714x814.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb9f428f9-ea1d-4718-a34f-a2919ae35b10_1714x814.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>‚Ä¶ and so does Vinterior.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png" width="483" height="213.6346153846154" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:644,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:483,&quot;bytes&quot;:139468,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3be5a6b0-63cf-4026-940d-20c9f1dfd356_1668x738.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Vinted, Vinterior, and eBay charge no seller fees now (note that Vinterior does charge 20% VAT to sellers). Vinted flags that paying VAT is not necessary if that you sell is <strong>less</strong> than the total that you buy. As mentioned, selling fees and gross take rates are quite complex, and will be the subject of a later newsletter edition (!).</p><h3>The climate question: unpacking impact in circular consumption</h3><p>Circularity enables three climate unlocks: carbon, water, and waste.</p><p><strong>Carbon</strong>. By reducing the need to manufacture new products, circular consumption decreases the carbon emissions associated with production and transportation. For example, buying a secondhand piece of clothing or a refurbished electronic device can significantly reduce its carbon footprint compared to buying new. Vinted publishes an <a href="https://press-center-static.vinted.com/Climate_Impact_Report_Summary_EN_2023_89b136c376.pdf">annual impact report</a> highlighting their carbon mitigation.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png" width="471" height="444.60775862068965" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:876,&quot;width&quot;:928,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:471,&quot;bytes&quot;:71037,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffe62c526-d365-4fa7-84b6-9bc7c798260c_928x876.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><strong>Water.</strong> The fashion &amp; electronics industry are notorious for their water consumption, specifically in textile production and rare earth mining. By extending the life of clothing &amp; electronics through resale or rental, we can mitigate the water usage associated with creating new garments. Backmarket includes a section on this in their <a href="https://www.backmarket.co.uk/en-gb/impact/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BM-IMPACTREPORT-ENG.pdf">impact report</a>.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png" width="415" height="497.63274336283183" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1084,&quot;width&quot;:904,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:415,&quot;bytes&quot;:274330,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F797f62d9-658e-4f44-aa83-31ee47849cba_904x1084.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><strong>Waste.</strong> Almost all consumer industries contribute significantly to waste. By extending the life of products, we can significantly reduce the amount of waste. See Ebay‚Äôs report on waste (upper RHS) below.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png" width="549" height="241.3186813186813" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:640,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:549,&quot;bytes&quot;:1033781,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad332bea-de32-4446-afa9-088b7046f58b_2126x935.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3>A note on reverse logistics</h3><p>An important step in enabling circular consumption is <strong>reverse logistics.</strong> This is the process of moving products from their final destination back to the seller or manufacturer for reuse, recycling, or refurbishment. One example here is UseAgain, which helps retailers re-use their glassware.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png" width="505" height="279.2067307692308" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:805,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:505,&quot;bytes&quot;:134754,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb5584656-b51f-4e6c-982f-6c7bf96e6c81_1476x816.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>We will be exploring this in more detail in Part 3 of this series - small foreshadowing!</p><h3>Can mass consumption be circular?</h3><p>As consumer awareness around sustainability continues to grow, the demand for circular consumption models is expected to increase. P2P platforms like eBay, Vinted, and Hurr are leading the charge by making it easier for consumers to buy, sell, and rent items in a way that reduces waste and lowers environmental impact.</p><p>Circularity (i.e. re-use, resale, rental) may not reach 100% of products, but we do believe that all products will need to be circular. We‚Äôll be exploring what this looks like next week when we look at Sustainable Brands, which have traditionally operated in the linear economy but are shifting their models to be more sustainable.</p><p>As always, get in touch if you‚Äôd like to debate or chat around this article. I‚Äôm at estia@ekavc.com üëã</p><div><hr></div><h3>Week in Impact Articles&nbsp;‚úçüèΩ</h3><p>Monday: <a href="https://medium.com/@kyeg/trust-and-reciprocity-are-the-foundations-of-all-economic-systems-d862edd56fc0">Trust and Reciprocity Are the Foundations of All Economic Systems.</a></p><p>Tuesday: <a href="https://heatmap.news/guides/zillow-climate-risk-flooding-fire?utm_campaign=heatmap_daily_free&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;_hsenc=p2ANqtz-9lFtqpRzdsRuVEFcPilNu_rpcYf8KCNjg1i0KY9UvZA0YSlBouVbzGsIjM9HpjZWoAOYo4G23GY-uLTjN5NAQskO9f1A&amp;_hsmi=329092814&amp;utm_content=329092814&amp;utm_source=hs_email">Should You Trust Zillow‚Äôs Climate Risk Data?</a></p><p>Wednesday: <a href="https://www.thediff.co/archive/offshoring-and-ai-agents/?ref=the-diff-newsletter">Offshoring and AI Agents</a></p><p>Thursday: <a href="https://www.edie.net/uk-businesses-asked-to-weigh-in-on-new-industrial-strategy-plans/?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=edie_daily_news_alert_14-10-2024&amp;utm_content=edie_daily_news_alert_14-10-2024+CID_c7bfef02457162530c4957b3fc2dd049&amp;utm_source=campaign%20monitor&amp;utm_term=UK%20businesses%20asked%20to%20weigh%20in%20on%20new%20industrial%20strategy%20plans">UK businesses asked to weigh in on new industrial strategy plans</a></p><p>Friday: <a href="https://www.edie.net/greenwashing-many-companies-are-repeat-offenders-study-finds/?utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=edie_daily_news_alert_11-10-2024&amp;utm_content=edie_daily_news_alert_11-10-2024+CID_7fdf394c0b118b2666a2ea33378eb0c9&amp;utm_source=campaign%20monitor&amp;utm_term=Greenwashing%20Many%20companies%20are%20repeat%20offenders%20study%20finds">Greenwashing: Many companies are repeat offenders, study finds</a></p><div><hr></div><h3>3 Key Charts&nbsp;<strong>üìä</strong></h3><h4>1. Are EVs forever? Not for everyone.</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe58c36b1-ae06-4ee7-beef-904778c04102_942x478.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe58c36b1-ae06-4ee7-beef-904778c04102_942x478.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe58c36b1-ae06-4ee7-beef-904778c04102_942x478.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/