tackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"><strong>Wanna be featured on eu.vc? Learn how <a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/submit-your-contribution-to-unfiltered">here.</a></strong></figcaption></figure></div></body></html>	Circular consumption offers an alternative to linear consumption by keeping goods in circulation for longer through reselling, renting, repairing, and recycling. This reduces the need for new resources, lowers waste, and minimizes environmental impact.	2024-10-16 23:14:09	2024-10-20 19:35:21.227	2024-10-20 19:51:05.858	{vc}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ac95c75-fd85-4488-8b7f-18426c47fae2_1839x760.png	anon	the-consumerisation-of-climate
233	https://www.usermag.co/p/the-black-insurrectionist-account	The ‚ÄòBlack Insurrectionist‚Äô account is run by a white man	+ Lily Allen's feet pic empire, Timoth√©e Chalamet crashes his own look alike contest, influencers are monetizing cancer, and more	<html><head></head><body><p>Over the past several months, an account on X called Black Insurrectionist has pushed a slew of viral conspiracy theories. The account‚Äôs profile photo is of a Black soldier with the tagline ‚ÄúI FOLLOW BACK TRUE PATRIOTS.‚Äù </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png" width="536" height="318.2236220472441" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:377,&quot;width&quot;:635,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:536,&quot;bytes&quot;:203698,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F24c24d6c-ff2b-49ef-8d61-18e0e925e102_635x377.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>The account has amassed over 352,200 followers  on X, in large part by pushing false information about Harris, Tim Walz, and boosting Trump, Vance, and their  Republican allies. </p><p>Brian Slodysko of the AP <a href="https://apnews.com/article/black-trump-kamala-harris-tim-walz-aca31c66fe5bfef1e8827581e7919ece">found the man who runs this account</a>, and it turns out he‚Äôs a white man from upstate New York. </p><blockquote><p>The Black Insurrectionist account is linked directly to Jason G. Palmer, who has his own questionable backstory, starting with the fact that he isn‚Äôt Black, according to an Associated Press review of public records, open source data and interviews with a half-dozen people who interacted closely with Palmer over the past two decades. </p><p>The records and personal accounts offer a portrait of an individual who has repeatedly been accused of defrauding business partners and lenders, has struggled with drug addiction and whose home was raided by the FBI over a decade ago. He also owes more than $6.7 million in back taxes to the state of New York.</p></blockquote><p>As I‚Äôve argued before, examples like this are why we desperately <a href="https://www.usermag.co/p/we-need-to-know-who-is-funding-the">need more transparency in the creator economy</a>.  </p><h2>Helen Mirren just wishes Kurt Cobain was alive to see all of this</h2><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp" width="1000" height="667" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:667,&quot;width&quot;:1000,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:172022,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/webp&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F38cd483e-e000-40b4-9837-2749f661cfeb_1000x667.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Helen Mirren recently <a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/lifestyle/helen-mirren-technology-ageing-flirting-fashion-russian-heritage-b1189849.html">gave an interview to Evening Standard</a> in which she talked about being ‚Äúsad‚Äù that Nirvana‚Äôs Kurt Cobain is no longer alive, because he never got the chance to experience GPS and its ‚Äúmagical‚Äù functionality.</p><p>‚ÄúI always say, it‚Äôs so sad that Kurt Cobain died when he did, because he never saw GPS,‚Äù said Mirren. ‚ÄúGPS is the most wonderful thing, to watch my little blue spot walking down the street. I just find it completely magical and unbelievable.‚Äù</p><p>The quote went viral because of how absurd it was. But what I think is more hilarious is <a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/helen-mirren-kurt-cobain-gps-1236190259/">how often Mirren seems to think about how Cobain would react to modern technology</a>. According to Variety, </p><ul><li><p>In 2014, she told&nbsp;Oprah Winfrey, ‚ÄúLook at Kurt Cobain ‚Äî he hardly even saw a computer! The digital stuff that‚Äôs going on is so exciting. I‚Äôm just so curious about what happens next.‚Äù</p></li><li><p>A year later, she told&nbsp;<a href="https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/beauty-hair/celebrity-hair-makeup/a37559/dame-helen-mirren-loreal-paris-interview/">Cosmopolitan</a>, ‚ÄúI was thinking about Kurt Cobain the other day and he died without knowing the internet, and I‚Äôm totally blown away by that.‚Äù</p></li><li><p>In 2016, she said to the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3400373/My-life-s-litany-mistakes-reveals-Dame-Helen-Mirren-wouldn-t-want-way.html">Daily Mail</a>, ‚ÄúIf I‚Äôd died at 27, the age that Kurt Cobain [of rock band Nirvana] died in 1994, I‚Äôd never have even known there was an internet! Incredible things are happening all the time and I can‚Äôt wait to see what comes next.‚Äù</p></li></ul><h2>‚ÄòThis being universally disliked‚Ä¶ feels like a culture shift‚Äô</h2><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png" width="520" height="496.940133037694" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:862,&quot;width&quot;:902,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:520,&quot;bytes&quot;:1176062,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98c49d90-0e93-451f-93b1-d59543940137_902x862.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Kim Kardashian <a href="https://x.com/popcrave/status/1848914937323679865?s=46">hosted a private screening of the movie musical Wicked</a> on Tuesday night joined by stars Ariana Grande and Cynthia Erivo. She showed off her entire house decked out in green and pink with thousands of roses, streamers, elaborate balloon arches, decorations and treats. The entire thing looked like a massive Instagram activation that would have gone viral in 2016. </p><p>This time around, however, people <em>hated</em> it. She got dragged to hell in the comments and all over Twitter for overconsumption and being out of touch. I think the reaction to the event and Kardashian‚Äôs IG posts shows how clearly the vibe in culture has shifted from a decade ago.</p><p>‚ÄúWe‚Äôre tired of rich people getting free things when they‚Äôre the only ones who can afford them in the first place,‚Äù one Twitter user <a href="https://x.com/tylerduran21/status/1849541875297845735">posted</a>, summarizing much of the critique.</p><p>‚ÄúThis being universally disliked‚Ä¶ feels like a culture shift,‚Äù YouTuber Tyler Oakley posted, ‚Äúthis isn't a personal attack on your fav, it's appreciation for the growth of the collective's class consciousness &amp; the outgrowth of a culture of celebrity worship &lt;3</p><h2>Blue MAGA is sharing false conspiracies about media hiding a Trump story</h2><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://x.com/shayan86/status/1850557259316613324?s=46" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png" width="534" height="434.62331838565024" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:726,&quot;width&quot;:892,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:534,&quot;bytes&quot;:391684,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/shayan86/status/1850557259316613324?s=46&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1bd6f18a-9ac7-4204-a800-fc0a4382725d_892x726.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Last week, a bunch of influential centrist liberal influencers began pushing a conspiracy theory about how the media is all colluding to hide a big ‚Äúsecret story‚Äù about Trump. I‚Äôm not even going to waste space debunking the many ways this conspiracy is deeply delusional, but suffice to say that if a media org isn‚Äôt running a blockbuster story that would undeniably amass them views and subscribers, it‚Äôs because that story doesn‚Äôt exist or they can‚Äôt confirm it. </p><p>The bigger issue here is that, <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2024/07/14/blueanon-conspiracy-theories-trump-rally-shooting/">as I wrote for The Washington Post this summer</a>, there is a rampant conspiracism problem in centrist liberal anti-Trump influencer spaces. </p><p>Trump is a threat to democracy and the media does far too much to normalize his dangerous ideology. They regularly launder his image, fail to hold him to the same standards as other politicians, and don‚Äôt report on him critically enough. But liberal internet users‚Äô have become increasingly comfortable adopting MAGA tactics and talking points in their efforts to attack him. </p><p>The phenomenon is known as BlueAnon, and in these centrist liberal anti-Trump influencers‚Äô world, shadowy forces, including the mainstream media, are all part of a coordinated plot destroy Kamala Harris‚Äô candidacy and usher Trump back into power.</p><p> Karl Folk, an independent researcher who studies authoritarianism and radicalization, said this ‚Äúmore conspiratorial mind-set has become more pronounced in liberal circles‚Äù in recent months. It‚Äôs an important reminder to be skeptical and question any unsourced claims built to feed into a preexisting belief system. </p><h2>New conservative grifter just dropped</h2><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png" width="488" height="736.9571106094808" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1338,&quot;width&quot;:886,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:488,&quot;bytes&quot;:1517466,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6af6a778-8e50-4fd8-81a5-bd9fbec68ae4_886x1338.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Maia Poet, a 25 year old Israeli-American, recently went viral for claiming that the Hamas attack on October 7th <a href="https://x.com/thepeacepoet99/status/1843036649179292098">made her detransition and abandon the LGBTQ community</a>. She claims that <a href="https://x.com/thepeacepoet99/status/1843036649179292098">not having enough have time to squeeze into her chest binder</a> in order to get to a bomb shelter after sirens broke out following the attack, awoke her to the ‚Äúgender lies‚Äù in liberal society. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png" width="608" height="175.54110898661568" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:302,&quot;width&quot;:1046,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:608,&quot;bytes&quot;:68499,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F53ebb362-29a6-43d1-bbf4-a5bcf9bb7d5b_1046x302.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Now she‚Äôs advising parents of LGBTQ youth to ‚Äú<a href="https://x.com/thepeacepoet99/status/1841910831367520720">send their kids to a war zone</a>‚Äù in order to ‚Äúcure‚Äù them of their ‚Äúgender ideology.‚Äù Poet‚Äôs entire feed is a mix of intense pro-Israel messaging and right wing misinformation about trans people. Her following is already up since going viral and now she has formally announced she‚Äôs backing Donald Trump. We‚Äôll see how far she goes. </p><h2><strong>An AI-powered transcription tool used in hospitals invents things no one ever said</strong></h2><p>OpenAI has claimed that its AI transcription tool Whisper has a near ‚Äúhuman level robustness and accuracy.‚Äù But an AP <a href="https://apnews.com/article/ai-artificial-intelligence-health-business-90020cdf5fa16c79ca2e5b6c4c9bbb14">investigation found</a> that in reality it makes up massive chunks of text and constructs entire conversations from thin air. </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg" width="520" height="446.48275862068965" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:996,&quot;width&quot;:1160,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:520,&quot;bytes&quot;:192436,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffb55367-13cd-4cf2-8b3c-4d5996782e57_1160x996.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>More than a dozen software engineers, developers and academic researchers have spoken out about the tool and claim it regularly hallucinates racial commentary, violent rhetoric and even imagined medical treatments.</p><p>This is a huge problem because Whisper is being in a growing number of industries globally, including <a href="https://apnews.com/article/chatgpt-ai-health-doctors-microsoft-f63d7fcc4b361cf8073406bf231e2b92">medical centers</a> to transcribe patients‚Äô meetings with doctors. </p><p></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.usermag.co/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.usermag.co/subscribe?"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><h2>What I‚Äôm reading</h2><p><strong>There‚Äôs something off about this year‚Äôs ‚Äúfall vibes‚Äù</strong> </p><p>Autumn is being eaten by a deluge of AI slop. - <em><a href="https://www.vox.com/culture/378855/ai-slop-fall-autumn-inspiration-vibes-pinterest">Vox</a></em></p><p><strong>The new dark money: How influencers get paid big bucks to court your vote</strong> </p><p>On TikTok, Instagram and X, freelance creators profit from the murky practice of persuading their large followings to back Trump or Harris. - <em><a href="https://archive.ph/2024.10.26-163614/https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2024/10/26/social-media-influencers-election-money-campaigns/#selection-545.0-549.139">WaPo</a></em></p><p><strong>How a tech mogul backed by JD Vance now bolsters Trump‚Äôs fortune</strong> </p><p>Trump relies on Rumble‚Äôs Chris Pavlovski for a key component of his media business. - <em><a href="https://archive.ph/2024.10.26-105409/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2024/10/26/trump-rumble-tech-pavlovski/#selection-685.65-685.71">WaPo</a></em></p><p><strong>I created a chatbot of myself and had it answer my Instagram DMs. Boy, was I annoying.</strong></p><p>Katie Notopolous discovered that her AI personality was peak millennial cringe and Meta‚Äôs bots aren't well-tested. - <em><a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/instagram-chatbot-i-created-dm-bad-personality-2024-10">Business Insider</a></em></p><p><strong>I am my own legal department: the promise and peril of ‚Äújust go independent‚Äù</strong></p><p>Independent publishing is one important facet of the media ecosystem, and while I love it, I know it is not the path for everyone. - <em><a href="https://www.citationneeded.news/i-am-my-own-legal-department/">Molly White</a></em></p><h2>More fun stuff</h2><p>Lily Allen <a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/lily-allen-onlyfans-feet-pictures-spotify-1236191247/">makes more money selling feet pics on OnlyFans</a> than she does through Spotify streams. </p><p>Timoth√©e Chalamet <a href="https://x.com/FilmUpdates/status/1850594869036896431">showed up to his own lookalike contest</a>. </p><p>The New York City government <a href="https://hellgatenyc.com/city-paved-over-bed-stuy-aquarium/">paved over the Bed-Stuy Aquarium</a> :(</p><p>Wellness influencers are <a href="https://x.com/this_is_mallory/status/1849598591087812876?s=46">using their cancer diagnosis to push dubious products</a>. </p><p>A fundamentalist christian influencer is <a href="https://x.com/lezscum/status/1849263716501520792/photo/2">going forward with her ectopic pregnancy</a> because she‚Äôs anti abortion and now facing the possibility of dying and leaving behind 7 other children.</p><p>A artist <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@jrdnstn">Jordan Stone‚Äôs surreal and melodic TikTok videos</a> have been called ‚Äúpost-corecore.‚Äù </p><div id="tiktok-ifram